HSPC Observation Status, basic

A set of codes that describe the state of the observation.

This value set includes codes from the following code systems:

  • Include these codes as defined in http://hl7.org/fhir/observation-status
    CodeDisplay
    finalFinalThe observation is complete and verified by an authorized person
    entered-in-errorEntered in ErrorThe observation has been withdrawn following previous Final release
    unknownUnknown StatusThe observation status is unknown. Note that "unknown" is a value of last resort and every attempt should be made to provide a meaningful value other than "unknown"

name: HSPC Observation Status, basic
description: A set of codes that describe the state of the observation.
